1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
To some, it's no more than wheels and cocks, cleverly marking time.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:15,000
While others may see what we see, the steel that we strengthen ourselves,

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
each carrot of gold that we forge.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Every single part, designed, shaped, polished by our own hands,

5
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:35,000
it takes constant care and countless skills, but above all, it takes time.

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:42,000
Only after hundreds of days of devoted work can we finally print this word on each single dial,

7
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,000
superlative.

8
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:57,000
The mark of our autonomy, our responsibility, our integrity.

9
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:09,000
For this is all we make, but we make it all so that in time, you can make it your own.

